<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038556" n="169r"/>
      <p><lb/>Ex iis, quas heri accepi <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>D.</abbr> Nepote tuo <rs type="person" key="GND">Antonio</rs><!-- ToDo für Matthias. Person in GND erfassen: Antonio, Neffe von Michelotti. -->, <rs type="letter" key="letterID">litteris</rs><!-- ToDo: Nachgewiesener Brief vom Neffen Michelottis --> Te bene va<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lere l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus intellexi; ego per gratiam Divinam quoque bona valetu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dine utor. Pergrata mihi fuit<del><del/></del> co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endatio <rs type="person" key="personID">Juvenis</rs><!-- ToDo: person erstellen. Deutscher Student, der in Padua in Jurisprudenz promoviert. --> illius
            <lb/><rs type="place" key="place_KON-deutsch">Germani</rs>, qui huc venturus est pro accipienda laurea in utroque
            <lb/>jure; si qua in re ipsi utilis esse potero, lubens faciam. Hac occa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sione Te rogo, ut mihi mittas<del>,</del> per <rs type="person" key="GND">juvenem</rs><!-- ToDo: Gleiche person wie oben --> istum, si nondum <rs type="place" key="GeoNamesID">Ve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>netiis</rs> profectus est, volumina illa qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> habes <rs type="keyword">Transactionum
                        <lb/>Anglicarum</rs><!-- Phil. Trans. -->, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> proxime remittam. Hodie mane <rs type="person" key="GND">Giaco<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mettus</rs> noster, quem ad sanam mentem rediturum non puta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bant, Oratione eleganti Professionem suam auspicatus est,
                              <lb/>superavitque omnium quasi expectationem. Nuper misi ad
            <lb/><abbr>Dnum</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117596027">Zendrinum</rs> <rs type="biblio">Solutionem</rs><!-- ToDo: Soluzione im Giornale de' letterati nachweisen (soll erst herausgegenben werden). --> meam <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_HBPWC42H">Problematis</rs><!-- ToDo: diese Publikation (Problema) von Nic. I B. ist im GLI bereits erschienen. --> <add>olim</add> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me
                              <lb/>propositi, ut eam<del>Italice factam</del> in sermonem vestrum trans<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1038557" n="169v"/>
<lb break="no"/>latam <rs type="keyword">Diario</rs><!-- GLI --> inserendam curaret, quam si videre cupias
            <lb/>Tecum co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicabit.</p> <closer><salute>Vale et me ut facis, amare perge.</salute>
                  <lb/><dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1719-03-16">16. Martii 1719.</date></dateline></closer>
      <postscript><p><abbr>P. S.</abbr> Saluto plurimum <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr>
            <lb/><rs type="person" key="GND">Antonium</rs><!-- Neffe Michelottis -->, cui pro <rs type="letter" key="letterID">epistola</rs><!-- ToDo: Nachgewiesener Brief vom Neffen Michelottis (siehe oben) --> sua maximas gratias ago.</p></postscript>
</div>
